OL,3,CDan Jarvis: I have 'big
OL,4,Cresponsibility' to get Armed Forces
OL,5,Cthe funds they need
OL,7,FNew Defence Secretary Dan Jarvis has
OL,8,Fvowed to get the armed forces the
OL,9,Ffunding they need after his
OL,10,Fpredecessor quit over the issue.
OL,12,FJohn Healey and armed forces minister
OL,13,FAl Carns resigned over the long-
OL,14,Fdelayed defence investment plan (Dip)
OL,15,Fon Thursday.
OL,17,FMr Jarvis told The Sunday Telegraph he
OL,18,Fhad a "big responsibility" towards
OL,19,Fsoldiers who risk their lives for the
OL,20,Fcountry.
OL,26,@zD@GOUzD@ZO]
