CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781394469
OL,3,CDan Jarvis: I have 'big
OL,4,Cresponsibility' to get Armed Forces
OL,5,Cthe funds they need
OL,7,FThe timing of the resignations of Mr
OL,8,FHealey and Mr Carns, along with two
OL,9,Fministerial aides, came at a moment of
OL,10,Fperil for Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,12,FMr Jarvis, himself a former soldier,
OL,13,Ftold the newspaper: "The defence of
OL,14,Four nation is a shared endeavour... I
OL,15,Fhave a big responsibility in that
OL,16,Fregard now, but so do all of those
OL,17,Fpeople who expose themselves to risk
OL,18,Ftonight, tomorrow, next week, and we
OL,19,Fowe them a debt of gratitude.
OL,26,@uD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781394469
OL,3,CDan Jarvis: I have 'big
OL,4,Cresponsibility' to get Armed Forces
OL,5,Cthe funds they need
OL,7,F"I have a responsibility now to them
OL,8,Fto make sure that they get what they
OL,9,Fneed, and people should be very clear
OL,10,Fabout my determination to fulfil those
OL,11,Fduties, to make sure that they do
OL,12,F(get) precisely what they need."
OL,14,FMr Carns signalled he would take part
OL,15,Fin any leadership contest on Saturday,
OL,16,Ftelling Times Radio: "If someone fires
OL,17,Fa starting pistol, I'm not afraid of
OL,18,Fgunfire."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]xD@VOUzD@IO]
