OL,3,CDan Jarvis: I have 'big
OL,4,Cresponsibility' to get Armed Forces
OL,5,Cthe funds they need
OL,7,FAndy Burnham, who hopes to return to
OL,8,FWestminster in the Makerfield by-
OL,9,Felection and has made no secret of his
OL,10,FLabour leadership ambitions, has
OL,11,Falready said he would not be
OL,12,F"squeamish" about reducing the welfare
OL,13,Fbill to fund defence spending.
OL,15,FThe Greater Manchester mayor said "the
OL,16,Fworld has changed" and it was
OL,17,F"obvious" the Government would have to
OL,18,Fadjust its assumptions about defence
OL,19,Fspending in response.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@KO]wD@cOUxD@RO]yD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
