PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781394469
OL,3,CDan Jarvis: I have 'big
OL,4,Cresponsibility' to get Armed Forces
OL,5,Cthe funds they need
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Conservative leader Kemi
OL,8,FBadenoch has written to potential
OL,9,FLabour leadership rivals, calling on
OL,10,Fthem to cut welfare spending and
OL,11,Fredirect the savings to defence.
OL,13,FMrs Badenoch offered Sir Keir, as well
OL,14,Fas his possible successors, her
OL,15,Fparty's support to get the necessary
OL,16,Flegislation through Parliament.
OL,18,FThe Prime Minister is likely to face
OL,19,Fdifficult questions about defence
OL,20,Fspending at the G7 when members met in
OL,21,FFrance on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
