OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781394469
OL,3,CDan Jarvis: I have 'big
OL,4,Cresponsibility' to get Armed Forces
OL,5,Cthe funds they need
OL,7,FHe spoke to Nato secretary general
OL,8,FMark Rutte about the Dip on Saturday
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,FA Downing Street spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"The Nato secretary general welcomed
OL,13,Fthe UK's increased investment in
OL,14,Fdefence as an important contribution
OL,15,Fto the alliance and to meeting the
OL,16,Fthreats we face."
